<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sobre a Equipe — AguaCalc</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f9ff; color: #1a1a2e; }

    nav {
      background: #0077b6; color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    }
    nav .brand { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; }
    nav .links { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; }
    nav a { color: #cde; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    nav a:hover { color: #fff; }
    nav .btn-sair {
      background: #c62828; color: #fff;
      border: none; border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 6px 14px; cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;
    }

    .container { max-width: 860px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; }

    .card {
      background: #fff; border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,119,182,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center;
    }
    h2 { color: #0077b6; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .subtitulo { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

    .team { display: table; width: 100%; border-spacing: 16px 0; }
    .member {
      display: table-cell; width: 33%; vertical-align: top;
      background: #f0f9ff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #d0e8f5;
    }
    .member img {
      width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover; border: 3px solid #0077b6; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .member h4 { margin: 10px 0 5px; color: #005f8e; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .member .ra { margin: 4px 0; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #666; }
    .member .curso { margin: 4px 0; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #666; }
    .member .papel {
      margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #0077b6;
      font-style: italic; border-top: 1px dashed #b0d8f0; padding-top: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="brand">💧 AguaCalc</div>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="/calculo">Calculadora</a>
      <a href="/sobre">Sobre</a>
      <a href="/help">Ajuda</a>
      <form method="POST" action="/logout" style="display:inline">
        <button class="btn-sair" type="submit">Sair</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>👥 Sobre a Equipe</h2>
      <p class="subtitulo">Projeto desenvolvido para a disciplina de Gerência de Configuração, Entrega e Integração Contínua — GCEIC26 — PUC-Campinas</p>

      <div class="team">
        <div class="member">
          <img src="/ana.jpg" alt="Ana Júlia" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120'">
          <h4>Ana Julia Matozo Rodrigues</h4>
          <p class="ra"><strong>RA:</strong> 23027461</p>
          <p class="curso">Engenharia de Software<br>PUC-Campinas</p>
          <p class="papel">API 1 — Consumo Diário<br>(POST /AGUA/consumoDiario)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="member">
          <img src="/hugo.jpg" alt="Hugo" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120'">
          <h4>Hugo Daniel Bosada Rodrigues</h4>
          <p class="ra"><strong>RA:</strong> 23909526</p>
          <p class="curso">Engenharia de Software<br>PUC-Campinas</p>
          <p class="papel">API 2 — Custo Mensal<br>(POST /AGUA/custoMensal)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="member">
          <img src="/leticia.jpg" alt="Letícia" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/120'">
          <h4>Letícia Lima da Silva</h4>
          <p class="ra"><strong>RA:</strong> 23918691</p>
          <p class="curso">Engenharia de Software<br>PUC-Campinas</p>
          <p class="papel">API 3 — Projeção de Economia<br>(POST /AGUA/economia)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
